'''Lech Walesa''' ({{ngî+pl|Lech Wałęsa}}; {{bd|1943-ngièn|9-ngie̍t 29-ngit||}}), [[Pô-làn]] [[Chṳn-chhṳ]] fa̍t-thung-kâ, [[Thòn-kiet Kûng-fi]] liâng-thô-ngìn, [[Pô-làn|Pô-làn Khiung-fò-koet]] [[Chúng-thúng]] (1990—1995). [[1981-ngièn]] "[[Sṳ̀-thoi Chha̍p-chì]]" ngièn-thu fûng-yùn ngìn-vu̍t, [[1983-ngièn]] tet-tó [[Nobel Fò-phìn-chióng]].

== Kâ-thìn ==
Lech Walesa chhai [[1969-ngièn]] kiet-fûn, yông-yuk pat-ke chṳ́-ńg.

